title: [Vornavis, Wooded Plains]
description: To the south, the path joins a major road running east to west.  To the north, a fork in the path leads into a less dense wooded area to the northeast and a dense forest to the northwest.  Breezes blow through the trees, and spots of moonlight break through the canopy of leaves overhead.
